git clone https://github.com/user/repo.git
24. Revert vs Rebase vs Merge
Revert: Creates a new commit that undoes changes.

Rebase: Rewrites history.

Merge: Combines branches with a merge commit.

27. Managing Code in GitHub
Use branches, pull requests, code reviews, protected branches, CI/CD.

28. GitHub Actions
CI/CD automation tool built into GitHub.

Use case: Run tests, build, deploy automatically on push/PR.

29. Webhooks for Jenkins
Configure GitHub webhook → triggers Jenkins job on push/PR.

Jenkins listens for events and executes pipelines.

